msgid ""
"Upgrades 2 units every turn for all players if any player knows this tech."
msgstr ""

#: data/royale/techs.ruleset:401
msgid ""
"Allows building several fusion based units. Not all fusion units are worth "
"the cost."
msgstr ""

#: data/royale/techs.ruleset:406
#, fuzzy
msgid "Advanced Espionage"
msgstr "Модерна авиация"

#: data/royale/techs.ruleset:412
