msgstr ""

#: data/royale/techs.ruleset:422
msgid "Allows the construction of unit cargo planes."
msgstr ""

#: data/royale/techs.ruleset:474
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Makes the upgrade cost of your units 20% less expensive. Robotics makes the "
"upgrade cost 30% less expensive."
msgstr ""

#: data/royale/techs.ruleset:581 data/sandbox/techs.ruleset:525
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Reduces the risk of plague in your cities by 30% of the base chance (this is "
"additive with the benefits of any buildings)."
msgstr ""

#: data/royale/techs.ruleset:728
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Allows Workers and Engineers to build airstrips, airbases, and buoys. "
"Upgrades 2 units every turn for all players once any player knows this tech."
