#: data/royale/techs.ruleset:767
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Allows Settlers, Migrants, Workers, and Engineers to upgrade mines to oil "
"wells on Desert and Glacier tiles, for an extra production point."
msgstr "Позволява на Заселниците да строят крепости."

#: data/royale/techs.ruleset:781 data/sandbox/techs.ruleset:708
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Allows Settlers, Migrants, Workers, and Engineers to upgrade irrigation "
"systems to farmland."
msgstr "Позволява на Заселниците да строят крепости."

#: data/royale/techs.ruleset:867 data/sandbox/techs.ruleset:785
#, fuzzy
