#: data/royale/units.ruleset:3133
msgid "Establishing trade routes is not enabled in this ruleset."
msgstr ""

#: data/royale/units.ruleset:3207
msgid ""
"Explorers can also perform some actions in another player's city, although "
"the unit disappears after the action is complete. This text is left here  as "
"a reminder that they could do this if the ruleset would allow it."
msgstr ""

#: data/royale/units.ruleset:3211
